ublic services and on its commercial activities. The effect further down the supply chain and in other markets means that initial BBC spending is ‘multiplied’ and its contribution to the econ</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">omy is more than £8 billion. </span></li></ol><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="10" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 25.1pt; text-indent:0pt"><a name="_GoBack"></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">The BBC as a PSB can play a vital role in encouraging innovation and quality in the arts and can promote British culture</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">through commissioning new, exciting drama and, as it does, </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">new pieces of music during the Proms.</span><br /><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></li><li style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; line-height:115%; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 25.1pt; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">The </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">NUJ’s submission to the consultation on Delivering Quality First include</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">d</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> research carried out by Howard Reed of </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">Landman</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt"> Economics.  His report is an analysis of the impact of the DQF proposals</span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic"> </span><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:12pt">on the UK economy (in particular the creative industries secto</span><sp